         Looks like the 2 major problems with the new SK spells for the necros are the lvl 49 pet and Lich.</P><P>By the time the SKs get this pet, you realise EoT will be outdated severely? Necros of this level will have, what, 5-6 pet upgrades already?<BR>Its just a logical progression, at lvl 58 we got the lvl 44 necro pet, and 6 lvls later we will get the lvl 49. It may be powerful and all in the low 50s, but in the high 60s it will be the usual green con pet doing subpar damage because of his low level the SKs always used to have, something way outdated that necros of the same level wouldnt use for any reason.</P><P>SKs get Lich.<BR>Its not a new ability, we got already Deathly Temptation at lvl 58, which is pretty much the same thing than Call of Bones.<BR>Many yell about the SK regen being superior to the necro regen, thus cutting on the hp loss from Lich. Its part true. But what you seem to ignore, its the SK mana regen isnt close to the necro mana regen (that is if the necros would still be using Lich at the lvl the SKs will, which is a totally laughable idea, given the necros will have several upgrades of that spell at this lvl).<BR>SKs are pullers and melee. We pretty much never sit down to med, we either run around looking for a mob to pull to the group or melee a mob. Necros on the other hand are sitting 80% of the time. This may look silly, but the play style of the classes is really different. SK mana regen just plain suck, we can never sit and med. With same mana regen, it takes around twice the time to a SK to recover the same mana than it does for a necro. Hell, with Lich a SK will recover around 200 mana/minute while a necro of this same level using the appropriate Lich type spell for his level will be well over 600mana/min. Fear me for i have Lich.</P><P>The necros may not get strong enough upgrades of their current spells with PoP, but looking at the SKs and saying we are a menace because we take your abilities is silly. A lvl 65 SK will have pretty much the spell power of a lvl 49 necro. Theres 16 levels of spells you have over us. Our best DoT will be Ignite Blood and our best lifetap will remain Drain Soul (the new PoP lifetaps for SKs all have insane recasts time, they arent upgrades to Drain Soul, and given we have to sacrifice 2 spell slots for agro spells, 1 for DP, 1 for our atk buff and another for Shroud of Death, we have no where near the room for a lifetap with 1-2 min recast, totally worthless to our class).</P><P><CENTER><IMG SRC="http://pages.infinit.net/kerosene/sigfinal.JPG"></CENTER><BR><CENTER><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1116">magelo</A>   <A HREF="http://www.evguild.org">E/V</A></CENTER><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
